# AEMS Frontend - Quick Access Guide

## Getting Started

### Access the Platform
```
URL: http://your-app.com/dashboard
```

## Main Navigation

### From Sidebar (Left Side)
- **Dashboard** - Overview of all metrics
- **Asset Registry** - Manage all assets
- **Work Orders** - Maintenance tasks
- **Inspections** - Inspection management
- **Spare Parts** - Inventory management
- **Financial Reports** - Financial analytics
- **Analytics** - Performance analytics
- **Categories** - Asset categories
- **Locations** - Asset locations
- **Audit Log** - Activity history
- **Users** - User management (Admin)
- **Roles & Permissions** - Role management (Admin)
- **Profile Settings** - Your profile
- **Settings** - Preferences

### From Top Navbar
- **Notifications** - Click the bell icon
- **Help** - Support and documentation
- **User Menu** - Click your profile avatar
  - View Profile
  - Change Password
  - Logout

## Key Features & URLs

| Feature | URL | Access Level |
|---------|-----|--------------|
| Dashboard | dashboard | All Users |
| Asset Registry | assets | Asset Manager+ |
| Create Asset | assets/create | Asset Manager+ |
| Edit Asset | assets/{id}/edit | Asset Manager+ |
| Work Orders | work-orders | All Users |
| Create Work Order | work-orders/create | Technician+ |
| Inspections | inspections | Inspector+ |
| Schedule Inspection | inspections/create | Inspector+ |
| Inventory | inventory | Inventory Manager+ |
| Financial Reports | reports/financial | Asset Manager+ |
| Analytics | reports/analytics | Asset Manager+ |
| Users | users | Admin Only |
| Roles | roles | Admin Only |
| Profile | profile | All Users |
| Categories | settings/categories | Admin+ |
| Locations | settings/locations | Admin+ |
| Audit Log | settings/audit-log | Admin+ |

## Common Tasks

### Add New Asset
1. Click "Asset Registry" in sidebar
2. Click "Add Asset" button (top right)
3. Fill in asset details
4. Click "Save"

### Create Work Order
1. Click "Work Orders" in sidebar
2. Click "New Work Order" button
3. Select asset and details
4. Assign to technician
5. Click "Create"

### Manage Users (Admin)
1. Click "Users" in sidebar
2. Search or filter users
3. Click "Edit" to modify
4. Click "Delete" to remove
5. Click "View" for details

### Update Your Profile
1. Click your avatar (top right)
2. Click "Profile Settings"
3. Edit information
4. Click "Save Changes"

### Change Password
1. Go to Profile Settings
2. Scroll to "Change Password"
3. Enter current and new password
4. Click "Update Password"

## Global Utilities (JavaScript Console)

### Make API Calls
```javascript
// Note: apiCall uses relative paths based on the app root
// Get dashboard data
await window.apiCall('dashboard')

// Get assets
await window.apiCall('assets')

// Create asset
await window.apiCall('assets', 'POST', {name: 'New Asset'})

// Update asset
await window.apiCall('assets/123', 'PUT', {name: 'Updated'})

// Delete asset
await window.apiCall('assets/123', 'DELETE')
```

### Show Notifications
```javascript
// Success
window.showToast('Success!', 'success')

// Error
window.showToast('Error occurred', 'error')

// Warning
window.showToast('Warning!', 'warning')

// Info
window.showToast('Information', 'info')
```

### Manage Modals
```javascript
// Open modal
window.openModal('assetModal')

// Close modal
window.closeModal('assetModal')
```

### Format Data
```javascript
// Format currency
window.formatCurrency(1000) // $1,000.00

// Format date
window.formatDate('2024-05-17') // May 17, 2024

// Format date & time
window.formatDateTime('2024-05-17T10:30:00')
```

## Dashboard Metrics Explained

| Metric | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| **Total Assets** | Sum of all assets in system |
| **Active Assets** | Fully operational assets |
| **Open Work Orders** | Pending maintenance tasks |
| **Total Asset Value** | Combined value of all assets |
| **Upcoming Inspections** | Inspections due in 30 days |
| **Under Maintenance** | Assets currently in maintenance |
| **Low Stock Items** | Inventory below reorder point |

## Status Colors

- 🟢 **Green** = Active / Success / Operational
- 🟠 **Orange** = Warning / In Progress / Maintenance
- 🔴 **Red** = Critical / Retired / Error
- 🔵 **Blue** = Info / Available / Pending

## Search & Filter

### Asset Registry
- **Search**: By name or code
- **Category**: Filter by type
- **Status**: Active/Maintenance/Retired
- **Location**: By location

### Users
- **Search**: By name or email
- **Role**: By user role
- **Status**: Active/Inactive

### Work Orders
- **Status**: Open/In Progress/Completed
- **Assigned To**: By technician
- **Asset**: By specific asset

## Mobile Tips

- Sidebar collapses on mobile
- Touch-friendly buttons
- Scrollable tables
- Responsive modals
- Optimized forms

## Keyboard Shortcuts

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `Esc` | Close modal |
| `Enter` | Submit form |
| `Tab` | Navigate form fields |
| `Ctrl+F` | Browser find (search page) |

## Troubleshooting

### Page Not Loading
1. Refresh browser (Ctrl+F5)
2. Clear cache
3. Check internet connection

### Form Not Submitting
1. Check for error messages
2. Verify all required fields filled
3. Check browser console for errors

### Modal Not Opening
1. Check browser console
2. Verify modal ID is correct
3. Try refreshing page

### Data Not Updating
1. Click refresh button
2. Wait 5 minutes for auto-refresh
3. Check API status

## Performance Tips

- Search/Filter on large datasets (pagination used)
- Data auto-refreshes every 5 minutes
- Use browser cache for faster loading
- Close unused modals to improve performance

## Security Reminders

- Log out when leaving computer
- Never share your password
- Report suspicious activity
- Enable two-factor authentication (if available)
- Keep browser updated

## Need Help?

1. Click **Help** in top navbar
2. Check documentation links
3. View **FRONTEND_GUIDE.md**
4. Check browser console (F12) for errors
5. Contact administrator

